{"tid":2351883,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！Tesla 未能達到去年出貨目標","createTime":"2021-01-03T14:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T16:21:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4bafc8d0a0a449a87041947fbec9a2c3553209","tid":2351883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"Tesla 向來都有相當樂觀的業績估算，而大多數情況都能夠實現，令投資者相當意外。不過去年他們為全年出貨總數定下的目標，卻差一點才可以達成。<br />\n<br />\nTesla 最近公佈，他們在 2020 年全年電動車出貨量為 499,500 部，其中高級型號 Model S/X 有 57,039 部，入門型號 Model 3/Y 則有 442,511 部，比他們之前定下的全年 50 萬部目標還差一點才可以達到。不過如果計算生產總數，則其實有 509,737 部，算是某程度上達到了目標有餘，只是部分產品未能及時離開工廠出貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/03/tesla-q4-2020-vehicle-production-deliveries/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2Ftesla-q4-2020-vehicle-production-deliveries%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0OgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=71c614b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/03/tesla-q4-2020-vehicle-production-deliveries/life-tech/auto/</a>"},{"pid":"d01988263dbe55b78f1b8e593b2f49b119b2f87f","tid":2351883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngreat drop tmr"},{"pid":"780a6cb0e52321582c0d23c2144d405e760cb7ab","tid":2351883,"uid":312920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d01988263dbe55b78f1b8e593b2f49b119b2f87f","tid":2351883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hk